# Repository Secrets (GitHub -> Settings -> Secrets and variables -> Actions -> Secrets)

# Azure-only template note:
# With OIDC federation enabled in azure/login, no client secret is required.
# This repository is passwordless by default for both CI and CD.
# Keep this file for optional future secrets, but none are required by default.

# Optional (only if your organization disallows OIDC and uses secret-based auth):
# AZURE_CREDENTIALS={"clientId":"...","clientSecret":"...","subscriptionId":"...","tenantId":"..."}
